data.text: Please RT this important safety training announcement for hurricane preparedness that’s designed specifically for individuals on the #autism spectrum living in South Florida. Thank you @UMNSUCARD for making this vital training available to individuals & families! @AutismTalkAspie https://t.co/POGFg66KAV

tweets.text: Is your family ready for #hurricaneseason? Join us for an informative workshop and learn how to prepare individuals with ASD for #hurricanes, #evacuation procedures and how to access Office of #Emergency Management (OEM) services. For more information: https://t.co/xsVXzX8sG5 https://t.co/6yTwjCVRej
